a-) Bölme aşaması:
[16, 21, 11, 8, 12, 22] -> [[16, 21, 11], [8, 12, 22]]
[[16,21,11], [8, 12, 22]] -> [[[16], [21, 11]], [[8], [12, 22]]]
[[[16], [21, 11]], [[8], [12, 22]]] -> [[[[16]], [[21], [11]]], [[[8]], [[12],[22]]]]
Birleştirme aşaması: 
[[[[16]], [[21], [11]]], [[[8]], [[12], [22]]]] -> [[[16], [11, 21]], [[8], [12, 22]]]
[[[16], [11, 21]], [[8], [12, 22]]] -> [[11, 16, 21], [8, 12, 22]]
[[11, 16, 21], [8, 12, 22]] -> [8, 11, 12, 16, 21, 22]
Sonuç: [8, 11, 12, 16, 21, 22]


b-) O(n log n)
